headline: Labcorp® Plasma Detect™ Clinical Studies Featured in Nature Medicine and Clinical Cancer Research
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, today announced Labcorp Plasma Detect, a tumor-informed, blood-based assay used to detect molecular residual disease (MRD) from circulating tumor DNA (ctDNA), was featured in two recent peer-reviewed publications – Nature Medicine and Clinical Cancer Research.
